# Onsite Engineering

- **Stack:** Quotation = HTML + Google Apps Script. Sales Intelligence = Next.js 16, FastAPI, Supabase.
- **BOQ CSV:** Header order exact. Serial numbers numeric only (1, 1.1, 1.1.1); no letters, hyphens. Child rows need parent. Units from valid list; numbers without commas.
- **User requirements:** (1) Weightage + engineering quantity for same item. (2) Financial: per entity equity + per bank interest (different rates/tenures, credit/debit balanced).
- **Refs:** `knowledge/boq-fix/SKILL.md`, `knowledge/onsite-platform-knowledge-base.md`, `docs/ONSITE_USER_REQUIREMENTS_DEMO.md`.
